++  bolo                                                ::  eyre state
    $:  wig=(map duct (list rout))                      ::  server routes
        ged=duct                                        ::  client interface
        giv=[p=@ud q=(map ,@ud duct)]                   ::  incoming requests
        ask=[p=@ud q=(map ,@ud ,[p=duct q=hiss])]       ::  outgoing requests
